'''Kizito Mihigo''' wavukiye i [[Kibeho]] tariki ya 25 Mukakara 1981, ni umuririmvyi w'umunyarwanda. Mu mwaka wa 1994, yarokotse ihonyabwoko ryakorewe abatutsi. Ise wiwe, umushingantahe Buguzi Augustin, yaragandaguwe mw'iryo honyabwoko.

Yize amashure yisumbuye mu iseminari ntoya y'i Butare mu Rwanda, aca abanfanya mu mashuri y'umuziki mu Buraya, mu ishuri rya [[Conservatoire de Musique de Paris]] mu gihugu c'Ubufaransa.
